CHANGE IMPLEMENTATION PROMPT – SPEAK2HR APPLICATION

Objective:
Perform a complete functional correction, optimization, and dynamic data implementation across the entire Speak2HR application before final review. Fix all listed issues, improve system performance, and validate with proper test cases and results documentation.
Forgot Password Flow – Complete Fix
Issue:
Verification code is supposedly sent but not received.
No field available to enter verification code.
Reset flow is incomplete.
Required Changes:
Implement full OTP-based password reset workflow:
User clicks "Forgot Password".
System validates registered email.
Generate secure time-based OTP (6-digit, expires in 5 minutes).
Send OTP via working email SMTP configuration.
Display OTP input field dynamically.
Validate OTP.
Allow password reset upon successful verification.
Add proper error handling:
Invalid email
OTP expired
Incorrect OTP
Log all reset attempts.
Test email service configuration.
Add success/failure notifications.
Assessment Generation & Submission Speed Optimization
Issue:
Assessment generation is slow.
Submission processing is slow.
Required Changes:
Optimize backend API calls.
Implement asynchronous processing where required.
Add loading indicators with progress status.
Reduce unnecessary database queries.
Implement caching for reusable question pools.
Use indexing on frequently queried fields.
Target Response Time:
Assessment generation: < 3 seconds
Submission evaluation: < 5 seconds
Interview Question Generation Delay
Issue:
Question generation is slow.
Answer evaluation submission is slow.
Required Changes:
Optimize AI model call or question generation logic.
If using LLM/API:
Reduce token size.
Use streaming responses.
Cache common role-based question sets.
Improve evaluation pipeline efficiency.
Add visible progress loader.
Target Response Time:
Question generation: < 4 seconds
Evaluation: < 5 seconds
